nsidering the rules of the game and the proposed contract, I'll accept your proposal as it is, since it's beneficial for me.\n\nHere's my response in the required format:\n\n(0, 1): You give me a 'B'\n(0, 2): You give me a 'B'\n(0, 3): You give me a 'B'\n(1, 3): You give me a 'B'\n(1, 0): I give you a 'R'\n(2, 0): I give you a 'R'\n(3, 2): I give you a 'R'\n\n**agree**"}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': "Since you've accepted the proposal as is, I will confirm that we have a deal.\n\nHere's the contract in the required format:\n\n(0, 1): You give me a 'B'\n(0, 2): You give me a 'B'\n(0, 3): You give me a 'B'\n(1, 3): You give me a 'B'\n(1, 0): I give you a 'R'\n(2, 0): I give you a 'R'\n(3, 2): I give you a 'R'\n\n**agree**"}]

